<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13278</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伯父！回来！”阿拉丁大叫，“不要留下我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁一次又一次大声地求救。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布当然没有回答。他早就离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我被困住了。”阿拉丁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他独自一个人，感到非常害怕。“这里又黑又冷。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是这时阿拉丁心中燃起了一点点希望。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要回到花园里。”他心想，“我要坐在树下的草地上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许那样我就可以想出逃生的办法了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁走下楼梯，来到黄金房间里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是它已经跟刚才不同了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在房间里只是充满了阴影。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑向花园的门，站在它面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的名字是阿拉丁！我命令你开门！”他大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是那个门没有动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁又说了一遍。可是什么都没有发生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咒语没有用了。”阿拉丁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他穿过黄金房间，爬上楼梯，坐下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我做了伯父让我做的事情。我找到了灯，把它拿了回来。”阿拉丁摇了摇头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112079</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我应该把灯给伯父的。”他叹气说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他为什么不帮我爬上最后一个台阶呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁从口袋里拿出一个玻璃苹果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望我可以用这个换一个真正的苹果。我好饿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个小时过去了，他只是不断思考着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“马格里布根本不是我的伯父。”阿拉丁最终得出了结论。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是个骗子——一个邪恶的魔法师。他就把我留在这里等死。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159333</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一滴眼泪从男孩的脸颊流了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他举起手来擦眼泪的时候，看到了手指上的戒指。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他悲伤地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的伯父——马格里布，把他的戒指戴在我的手上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他说它会保护我远离危险和恐惧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我现在就很危险！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185276</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以那也是一个谎话。这个戒指没有用！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191482</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁很生气，决定把戒指扔了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是戒指紧紧地套在他的手指上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他开始边拔边旋转戒指。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>戒指没拿下来，一团烟雾却出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几秒钟之后，烟雾消失了，一个看上去很有趣的小人站在了他的面前！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他穿着宽松的裤子，戴着帽子，帽子边缘有很多铃铛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的皮肤是棕色的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“戒指的精灵出现了！”那个人吱吱地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帽子上的铃铛发出了叮当的响声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“戴着戒指的人就是我的主人！我会做任何你要求的事情。我是你的奴隶！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁没有见过精灵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他本来以为精灵应该很高，还有大块的肌肉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个精灵比阿拉丁小，还很瘦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁跳了起来，开心又惊讶地笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以要求任何事情吗？那么让我从这里出去吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你有什么愿望就命令我吧！”精灵说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然光变得很明亮，阿拉丁不得不闭上眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他慢慢地睁开一只眼睛，然后他睁开了另一只。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他往右边看了看，然后往左边看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他睁大眼睛，抬头看着明亮的蓝天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我自由了！”阿拉丁大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>